text: Singhal or “ _Singal_ ” is a predicated gotra of Jat by origin while for other aspecting factors its an variated form of Singla which were also found among the non Kshatriya‌ community of vaishya tradition. which oftentimes prevailed among the lower profiled baniya class of Jind state == References == Category:Jat clans of Punjab Category:Social groups of Gujarat Category:Social groups of Punjab
title: Singhal
